Vol / Page: 3
Edition:
Quote: The Warden (Mr McCarthy) has found that the title to a certain: special claim of 99 acres granted to the defendant Mein by another Warden (Mr Stratford) was obtained by fraudulent misrepresentation, and has ordered that the claim be forfeited.
